---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="Baptism" description="Ready to take the next step? Baptism is a public declaration of your faith in Jesus Christ.">
  <PageHero title="Baptism" image="/hero/1.jpg" />

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro">
        <h2>What is Baptism?</h2>
        <p>Baptism is an outward expression of an inward change. It's a public declaration that you have accepted Jesus Christ as your Lord and Savior. Through baptism, we identify with the death, burial, and resurrection of Jesus.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-baptism">
        <h3>Why Get Baptized?</h3>
        <div class="reasons-grid">
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>Jesus Commands It</h4>
            <p>Jesus instructed His followers to be baptized as an act of obedience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>Public Declaration</h4>
            <p>It's a way to publicly share your decision to follow Jesus with your community.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>Spiritual Milestone</h4>
            <p>Baptism marks a significant moment in your spiritual journey.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signup-section">
        <h2>Ready to Be Baptized?</h2>
        <p>We'd love to celebrate this step with you! Sign up and we'll reach out with next steps.</p>
        <a
          href="https://rolhenry.churchcenter.com/people/forms/1102414"
          data-open-in-church-center-modal="true"
          class="btn btn-large"
        >
          Sign Up
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<script src="https://js.churchcenter.com/modal/v1"></script>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .page-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .intro h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .why-baptism {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .why-baptism h3 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reasons-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reason {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reason h4 {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .reason p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .signup-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .signup-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .signup-section > p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .btn-large {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-teal);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-large:hover {
    background: var(--color-teal-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
